Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.31,0:00:17.23,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,喰君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.01,0:00:19.88,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,彩虹…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.85,0:00:23.03,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,我…想去那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.64,0:00:25.80,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,那也許是嘉祿 我想過去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.38,0:00:28.44,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,説的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.87,0:00:32.24,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,這就像是在邀請我們去一樣 讓人感到不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.11,0:00:33.91,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.24,0:00:41.72,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,還真是單純啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:43.94,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,就這麽不想讓我們靠近麽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.06,0:00:50.32,KHJ_TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(638,292)}第 1 3 譜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.06,0:00:50.32,KHJ_TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,480)}狂 歡 節
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.36,0:00:56.24,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,花礫君
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.91,0:01:02.62,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,薔薇之牆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.97,0:01:25.69,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,這對於花礫君來説太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.31,0:01:31.61,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,我立刻就送你回船上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.28,0:01:39.07,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,你…要到彩虹那裡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.74,0:01:40.32,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.28,0:01:42.08,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊肯定…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.08,0:01:43.91,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我礙手礙腳的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.70,0:01:45.83,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,從剛才起…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.08,0:01:49.92,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,我根本就是…跟不上你的節奏…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.34,0:01:55.80,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道自己超級礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:03.93,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 請帶我去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.56,0:02:06.23,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.73,0:02:11.81,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,花礫君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:16.82,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,花礫君…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.11,0:02:21.12,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,其實啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.49,0:02:26.16,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,我也非常希望花礫君能來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.54,0:02:31.17,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,一起走吧 去救小無
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.38,0:02:35.09,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,糺 你現在處於混亂狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.51,0:02:38.30,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,你應該意識到自己説了什麽奇怪的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.63,0:02:41.26,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,我們很弱的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.93,0:02:46.27,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,就連對馮德的生物們呵護備至的村野
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.81,0:02:49.19,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,也渴望著能力者的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.48,0:02:55.90,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,以我的名義準備了藥的人是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:02:58.65,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,提起燭醫生的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.78,0:03:00.99,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都很信任呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:04.87,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想對你動粗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:07.37,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想讓你跟我一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.71,0:03:13.58,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,平門
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:16.75,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,燭…燭醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.34,0:03:20.17,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常憧憬你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.72,0:03:23.51,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,一直…嚮往著你那樣強大的心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.05,0:03:24.97,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.89,0:03:28.06,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,爲什麽你要那麽優秀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:30.81,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,爲什麽你要存在在這世上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:35.94,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,我討厭這個卑微又惹人厭的自己 同時也討厭你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:41.45,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,隸屬國家防衛機關 研案塔 生命室的糺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:43.53,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,謀反罪是重罪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:46.53,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,你若反抗則立刻處以死刑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:47.79,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,平門 住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.62,0:03:52.08,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 糺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.26,0:04:01.97,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,爲了得到切實的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.88,0:04:04.18,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,暫時放他一馬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.26,0:04:08.76,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,不管他跑到哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.22,0:04:10.89,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,一三郎都不會停止追他的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.61,0:04:16.61,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,糺…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:23.36,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:52.56,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,終焉迷宮幻境
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:16.21,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 請别來妨礙我啊 小朔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:21.55,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,紀一 辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:29.97,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,手下留情？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.47,0:05:35.85,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,使用帽子的「束縛」技且不想至物件於死地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:38.35,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,因此調整了施與的壓力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:40.69,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,就拿現在來説
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:45.32,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,這施加於我一人的 不威脅生命只封鎖行動的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.44,0:05:46.90,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,就是現在所維持的平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.57,0:05:50.24,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我在封鎖的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:53.83,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,就已順利在腹部下方開了個洞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.95,0:05:58.29,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,用於召喚我的僕人們的洞穴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:00.50,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,提高壓力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.09,0:06:02.25,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,愚蠢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:07.26,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,平衡破壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:19.65,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,僅憑對帽子少女的遠程操作就想捕獲我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:24.94,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,看來我真是被輪之二艇艇長小看了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:28.86,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,天空中放出的虹之光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.03,0:06:32.07,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,正吸引著輪的蝦兵蟹將們的靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:36.00,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,就讓我將他們一網打盡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:38.79,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,二位要不要也過去那邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:42.54,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 那是我們的臺詞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:44.84,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,切 真礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.06,0:07:00.73,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:02.23,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,别混人視聽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.36,0:07:04.40,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,你剛剛差點啪地…啪地抽中我們誒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.44,0:07:05.40,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,千鈞一髮啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:07.32,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,與儀 花礫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.19,0:07:08.69,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.57,0:07:11.03,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,小無~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:12.82,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,嚇到了嗎 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.82,0:07:14.16,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,别放鬆警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:16.70,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,彩虹的源頭 看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.99,0:07:17.87,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,就在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:24.79,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉祿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:32.68,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,躺在母親懷抱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:35.05,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,是否很想入眠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:38.14,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,於門扉緊閉前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:41.77,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,賜予你們永眠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:43.48,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,原來還有時限的麽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.48,0:07:46.23,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,喰君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.49,0:07:52.41,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡交給我解決
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:54.07,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:33.86,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:45.79,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,與儀！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:47.63,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,薔薇之牆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.18,0:08:58.80,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,伊娃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:03.18,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,津久茂醬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:05.14,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑 無
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:08.23,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,要趕上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.69,0:09:09.73,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,要趕上！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:17.82,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,跟隨空氣中流淌的温柔聲響
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:19.62,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,到這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:22.91,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是巨大的貝殻内部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:27.71,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,微弱的振翅之音也得以共鳴 回蕩出動人旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:31.30,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是一無所有的空間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.71,0:09:32.88,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有你前往
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.26,0:09:34.72,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,就會誕生奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:40.55,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,交出門的鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.31,0:09:43.89,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,若你不從 則立刻…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:46.23,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,砍下你的頭顱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.53,0:09:54.53,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,送葬的輪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:56.45,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,眼下情形
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.86,0:09:59.11,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,對我們來説便是神秘之盒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:03.41,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,能將其打開的 只有在那内側持有鑰匙的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.99,0:10:04.83,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,你説什…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.69,0:10:33.27,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,無
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.44,0:10:37.28,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉…祿…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:47.83,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉祿！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:52.92,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,無
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:55.55,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉祿 你還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.59,0:10:58.47,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,傷口没事嗎 你還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:02.05,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是…嘉祿…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.26,0:11:04.93,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,話説回來…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:06.39,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:09.10,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 無
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:11.15,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麽倒在那裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:13.40,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,你爲什麽看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:16.65,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,身體動不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.11,0:11:21.45,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,我説啊 把這個送給花礫可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:27.12,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,快發出聲音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:26.70,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}他救我的時候 我跟他説好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:30.62,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,無！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:32.12,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,很可疑吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:33.29,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,你這笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:38.30,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉祿？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.76,0:11:39.63,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉祿！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:42.22,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉祿…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:43.55,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,血…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.39,0:11:45.80,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,渾身是血…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:49.35,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,想在最後再讓你們見上一面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.85,0:11:51.81,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,爲了替他了卻這一心願
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:53.23,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,才把無叫了過來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:55.65,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,「趕快來哦」這樣呼喚著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.15,0:11:59.28,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,能見到你他很幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.28,0:12:03.86,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,本應該在什麽的都没有的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.91,0:12:06.74,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,了結他的生命的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:10.37,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,很高興初次見到你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.12,0:12:14.46,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,因爲我和無只是説過話而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:19.38,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 和無一起在虹之森生活過的嘉祿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:21.59,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,現在也在我的體内
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.84,0:12:24.51,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是嘉祿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.84,0:12:29.81,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,無 已經破爛的衣服是不會再穿了的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:32.14,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,和那個是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:34.69,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是嚇到你了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.36,0:12:37.98,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,過來 無
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:40.44,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,能來到這裡還真是了不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.24,0:12:44.24,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,無待在我們這邊才是正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.74,0:12:47.70,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 手 給我抬起來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:50.41,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,和花礫君好好告别吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.99,0:12:53.83,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不可能和他永遠在一起的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.42,0:12:56.58,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.67,0:13:02.01,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,無 你真不懂事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:06.18,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,只要毁了花礫君 你就不會再有迷戀了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.01,0:13:07.97,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.35,0:13:09.39,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,别小看人了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:19.06,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 脈搏…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:21.57,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,真是没辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.94,0:13:27.24,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,如果還想玩的話 我會等著你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:31.33,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟我很寬容啊 無
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:48.01,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,盡情地玩耍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.14,0:13:52.68,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,不獲得我們的許可就擅自發動攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.93,0:13:57.90,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,知不知道我們爲了善後引起了多大的混亂啊 輪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.19,0:14:03.32,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,這次的事件都起於我的個人意願 我會承擔責任
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:07.49,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,話雖如此 表示支持的我也要負同責
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:09.11,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我們對此事抱有覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:12.16,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,但也請各位稍微注目一下此事的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:13.54,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,還説結果？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:15.33,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,别給我開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:18.37,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,不僅連帕魯内德的身影都没捕捉到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.46,0:14:22.88,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,而那個帕魯内德還把這次事件歸結爲黑白的單獨行動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:25.46,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,聲稱自己是清白的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.80,0:14:28.09,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,那個黑白現在也讓他逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.30,0:14:32.43,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至連定罪爲叛黨的糺也不知所蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.14,0:14:38.06,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,説起來 報告所説的救出物件嘉祿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.77,0:14:41.27,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,搬回來的時候已經處於心肺停止狀態的嘉祿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:44.44,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,在燭醫生的救治下已經恢復生命跡象
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.19,0:14:48.03,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,但還未恢復意識
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:53.49,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉祿…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:15:01.21,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,無君 我們暫且先回到船上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.17,0:15:10.26,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,所以説
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:13.43,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,我在問你到底有没有就算没有戶籍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.43,0:15:18.60,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,也可以特許進入的方法啊測試什麽的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.85,0:15:20.39,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,政府的學校嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:23.15,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,你想在那裡學到什麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.86,0:15:29.24,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,我對能力者啊火不火之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:30.90,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,真的超級討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.07,0:15:35.33,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,把椿給殺了 把夜鷹也殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.41,0:15:39.66,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,讓燕還有無一次又一次地流淚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:43.08,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的已經超級火大了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.26,0:15:50.38,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,一開始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.17,0:15:52.22,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,我以爲只要待在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.59,0:15:56.26,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,就能趁機報復火不火的那些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.31,0:15:58.31,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 總覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.93,0:16:01.10,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,我在這裡卻完全没有幫上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:03.94,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是太遜了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.81,0:16:08.65,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我要正經地學到一些技術獲得一些資格
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:10.82,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,變得可以戰勝能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:15.37,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠堂堂正正地和你們站在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.87,0:16:19.83,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 讓我工作啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.33,0:16:21.54,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,幹嗎突然大吼大叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:24.37,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是安安靜靜地好好聽著的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.71,0:16:26.67,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,就算翻遍了所有的書
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.00,0:16:30.30,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,没有一本寫著怎樣才能讓没有戶籍的人入學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:32.34,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:37.26,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,那麽 我就開個後門 讓你去學校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:42.27,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這只是作爲將你牽扯進來的人所要負的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.10,0:16:46.36,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,這以後的一切就都要靠你自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.40,0:16:48.36,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,可不是什麽簡單事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.44,0:16:52.86,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,你有没有能力在我們的世界登場
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.53,0:16:54.53,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,有待你自己去證明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:16:58.78,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事情是一定的！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:11.38,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,不在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:17.01,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,在去煙霧公館之前和平門先生談過話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:19.14,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,雪雪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:22.27,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 我希望和大家一起待在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:24.48,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.48,0:17:27.23,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,無君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.23,0:17:28.98,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,與儀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.94,0:17:33.82,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,很好啊 因爲是花礫選擇的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.11,0:17:40.45,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,在花礫君問我二號艇的孩子是什麽意思的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.03,0:17:42.83,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的非常擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.83,0:17:49.25,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,因爲 我們 已經不存在於這個世界上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.38,0:17:54.55,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,在成爲輪的時候 爲了保護家人的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:17:56.80,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,爲了不成爲他們的枷鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.47,0:17:59.47,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,連戶籍和資料都被修改了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:04.18,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,只有這裡才是我們的歸宿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.98,0:18:06.98,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,就算在外面遇到了很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:08.65,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,就算和他們變得要好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:11.86,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,最終大家都只是擦肩的過客
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.86,0:18:19.66,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,所以啊 小無和花礫君來這裡的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.74,0:18:22.49,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的非常高興
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.20,0:18:26.08,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像外面的空氣一下子吹拂過來一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.29,0:18:27.46,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,非常激動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.54,0:18:32.34,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 花礫君從今以後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.34,0:18:34.17,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要在外面經歷更多的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:37.13,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,和許多重要的人相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.97,0:18:39.68,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:13.34,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,花礫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.25,0:19:13.34,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}花礫君！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.55,0:19:17.42,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:20.59,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,花礫君…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.93,0:19:22.89,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,花礫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:26.47,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,不能哭 花礫君會困擾的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.02,0:19:29.18,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,花礫君…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.85,0:19:31.35,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,今後就把這個當做是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.35,0:19:34.11,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,有痛苦的事情一定要對它傾訴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.11,0:19:36.73,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,你會對這種東西説話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.23,0:19:38.78,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,花礫君 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:44.49,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,我的手還是有點拙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.12,0:19:47.04,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,這是和無君一起做的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:51.00,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,虹的布娃娃 把它當成是無君吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.04,0:19:53.92,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,醜死了 臉都扭曲成這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:56.71,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:20:00.26,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,花礫 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.22,0:20:07.56,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉祿還昏迷著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.52,0:20:12.94,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話 到下次見面之前幫我問問他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.31,0:20:14.98,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是可以把這個給我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.65,0:20:19.32,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,我會一直呼喚嘉祿的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:23.91,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,花礫君！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.57,0:20:28.91,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我再也見不到你了怎麽辦！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.95,0:20:30.37,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,與儀 無君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.45,0:20:31.62,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.67,0:20:36.33,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你們給我等下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.17,0:20:39.50,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是覺得我絕對得不到資格
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.75,0:20:43.26,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,回不來是不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:46.68,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,我就不能回來麽…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:51.64,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,資格…是什麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.06,0:20:54.19,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,你們没聽混蛋四眼説嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.48,0:20:57.90,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,難道説平門他故意…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.74,0:21:04.57,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,你性格還真是壞透了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.07,0:21:10.58,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,平門先生之所以會牽扯上花礫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.91,0:21:12.75,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,是因爲他當初在那艘船上待過對麽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:14.12,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,船？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:16.79,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,就是火不火的那艘試驗船
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.63,0:21:21.17,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,憑著好運在那次事件中撿回一條命的花礫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.76,0:21:26.89,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,經歷一段時月後偶遇到無 並最終被帶到了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.43,0:21:30.22,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是所謂的奇跡邂逅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.31,0:21:35.44,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的事情以一種奇特的形態被聯結在了一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.81,0:21:38.52,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,無的存在本身
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.94,0:21:41.86,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,也可能是被製造出的必然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.21,0:21:59.13,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.59,0:22:04.42,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麽了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.60,0:22:18.85,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,花礫 變温暖了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.94,0:22:19.94,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.90,0:22:30.41,KHJ_SUB,NTP,0,0,0,,再見啦！混蛋小動物！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:25.78,KHJ_ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}Be my reason
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.28,0:20:28.33,KHJ_ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}全てが今
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:30.70,KHJ_ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}Be my power,future
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.70,0:20:32.16,KHJ_ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}動き出す
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:33.46,KHJ_ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}Be my reason
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:35.96,KHJ_ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}君の傍で
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:38.34,KHJ_ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}Be my power,future
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.46,0:20:48.05,KHJ_ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}感情の名前なんて 言い出せばきりがないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.05,0:20:56.10,KHJ_ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}君の目が叫ぶのなら 本能で聞き分ける(Trust)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.10,0:20:57.98,KHJ_ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}つきまとう（Trash）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.98,0:20:59.23,KHJ_ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}そこにある
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.23,0:21:02.82,KHJ_ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}光も闇も
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.82,0:21:06.66,KHJ_ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}つながりだす ピースのように
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:10.95,KHJ_ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}理由があるから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.37,0:21:15.17,KHJ_ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}偶然でも　成り行きでも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.17,0:21:19.84,KHJ_ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}信じたい出會いに変わってく
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.92,0:21:26.64,KHJ_ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}心の温度が　少しずつ上がるね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.64,0:21:30.47,KHJ_ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}見せかけじゃない　駆け引きもない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.47,0:21:35.19,KHJ_ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}本當の自分のままで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.19,0:21:38.98,KHJ_ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}選んだ場所に立ってること
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.02,0:21:42.65,KHJ_ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}君に伝えたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.65,0:21:44.03,KHJ_ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}Be my reason
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.44,0:21:46.40,KHJ_ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}君の傍で
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.40,0:21:48.66,KHJ_ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}Be my power,future
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:25.78,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}Be my reason
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.28,0:20:28.33,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}世間萬物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:30.70,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}Be my power,future
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.70,0:20:32.16,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}於此始動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:33.46,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}Be my reason
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:35.96,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}伴君左右
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:38.34,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}Be my power,future
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.46,0:20:48.05,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}若要喚出情感之名 則無休無止無窮無盡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.05,0:20:56.10,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}你的眼神傳來呼喚 我以本能即可分辨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.10,0:20:57.98,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}相伴相隨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.98,0:20:59.23,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}不離不棄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.23,0:21:02.82,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}無論光明抑或黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.82,0:21:06.66,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}如緊湊相連的拼圖零片
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:10.95,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}一切皆有其因果
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.37,0:21:15.17,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}萍水相逢也好 命中註定也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.17,0:21:19.84,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}終將指引我們走向所堅信的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.92,0:21:26.64,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}赤誠真心 逐步升溫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.64,0:21:30.47,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}無虛情假意 非利益所趨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.47,0:21:35.19,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}以真實自我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.19,0:21:38.98,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}立於所盼之地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.02,0:21:42.65,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}願君側耳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.65,0:21:44.03,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}Be my reason
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.44,0:21:46.40,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}伴君左右
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.40,0:21:48.66,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}Be my power,future
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.50,0:22:07.97,KHJ_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,ありふれた展開なら　安心てワケじゃないだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.50,0:22:07.97,KHJ_ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,司空見慣的劇情走向 也無法讓人絲毫鬆懈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.05,0:22:16.10,KHJ_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,くり返す覚悟の連鎖　強くもなれるさ（cloud）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.05,0:22:16.10,KHJ_ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,重複與磨練中構築覺悟 終究變得堅韌頑強
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.14,0:22:18.19,KHJ_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,そらさずに（crash）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.14,0:22:18.19,KHJ_ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,不躲藏不回避
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.19,0:22:22.98,KHJ_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,もう何もごまかさないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.19,0:22:22.98,KHJ_ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,也別想蒙混過關
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.98,0:22:30.82,KHJ_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,受け取るんだ自分に似合う　眩しい未來を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.98,0:22:30.82,KHJ_ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,坦誠接受適於自己的 耀眼未來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.49,0:22:35.29,KHJ_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40}不器用なプライドその先のプライド　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.49,0:22:35.29,KHJ_ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40\an3}略顯笨拙的自尊 從今往後的尊嚴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.33,0:22:40.00,KHJ_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40}見つけたい笑顔を照らして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.33,0:22:40.00,KHJ_ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40\an3}只願點亮你的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.00,0:22:46.76,KHJ_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40}僕らは必ずそこに辿り著くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.00,0:22:46.76,KHJ_ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40\an3}我們定將到達彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.76,0:22:50.47,KHJ_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40}気まぐれじゃない気休めもない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.76,0:22:50.47,KHJ_ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40\an3}不是一時興起 不會放下警惕　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.47,0:22:55.22,KHJ_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40}精一杯の今を走れ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.47,0:22:55.22,KHJ_ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40\an3}付出一切奔跑於當下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.22,0:23:02.73,KHJ_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40}かさなりあうベクトルに　意味を感じながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.22,0:23:02.73,KHJ_ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40\an3}於向量交合處 體味真諦
